Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, girls! Don't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I was a little filly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:08.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the sun was going do-o-o-own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:09.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tell me she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The darkness and the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.99,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They would always make me fro-o-o-own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:15.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:17.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'd hide under my pillow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From what I thought I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:22.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Granny Pie said that wasn't the way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To deal with fears at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:28.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She said: "Pinkie you gotta stand up tall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Learn to face your fears
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll see, that they can't hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:35.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just laugh to make them disappear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ha! Ha! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So, giggle at the ghostly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:45.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Guffaw at the grossly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Crack up at the creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:49.67,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whoop it up with the weepy-y-y
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Chortle at the kooky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:53.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Snortle at the spooky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.04,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And tell that big dumb scary face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To take a hike and leave you alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.21,0:00:57.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if he thinks he can scare you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.34,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then he's got another thing coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,and the very idea of such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,just makes you wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:08.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Laugh!